{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e1fc1b44f0","title":"给王大海的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ffe7bccff5","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":4,"articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2b3ac145af","name":"赵悔深"},{"id":"9ec5840208","name":"河南"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0afed447ec","type":"title","text":"给王大海的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"e662d4b817","type":"authors","text":"河南赵悔深","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"be8b97c4e9","type":"subtitle","text":"(王大海：作家，《奔流》编辑，河南省文联常委；赵悔深:《河南日报》副刊主任，河南省文联副主席)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"c274978f58","type":"appellation","text":"大海同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"83c5c2beed","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十四日来信读到。在这之前，曾收到你的信，当时觉得你很快就要离开河南，就没有立刻给你写信。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"29eab0bd66","type":"paragraph","text":"你能够到鲁迅先生的故乡，而且就在鲁迅纪念馆，真值得羡慕，我希望你尽可能多住些日子，最好就在绍兴就近执笔写，一回至家，东一扯西一扯，印象一淡，便和在绍兴大不相同了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"6d0910efac","type":"paragraph","text":"几年来，生活的风暴，给人以复杂的严酷的考验。你的情况，我从朋友们的口中，你给苏鹰的来信中，知道一些。生活是严峻的，它不辜负坚持真理的人。我只有遥遥伸出手，无言的祝贺你的胜利。现在我想，即使我们一声不响，有些人也会内心惶愧不安吧，生活的无情的镜子，照出了每个人的真面目。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"d562be2c5e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们这里，正在整风。潮水似的意见，正打向统治了人们许多年的教条主义、宗派主义。从最近几天的长江日报上，可以看出一些轮廊。河南也动起来了。我希望你毫不迟疑的拿杂文的武器，参加目前这个轰轰烈烈的战斗。我现在照料“长江文艺”，迫切希望你为刊物写稿。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"9f05a24c94","type":"appellation","text":"敬  礼","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"4a0954e963","type":"paragraph","text":"秀玉同志问你的好","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"c56372419c","type":"paragraph","text":"盼有短信","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"0d27ea29e8","type":"paragraph","text":" 悔深  六月四日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"},{"id":"4e6af2f99f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《苏金伞右派集团言论与作品》（河南省文学美术工作者联合会，1958年）。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0"}],"page":{"id":"e03ffe23d7","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e1fc1b44f0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}